title: Morning Glory Bakery and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out, Bakery
description: Conscious kitchen serving vegan and vegetarian breakfast and lunch. Vegan, wheat-free, sugar-free baked goods, monthly organic specials, house-made breads, vegan french toast, waffles, biscuits and gravy, tofu scramble, vegan omelets, sandwiches, soups, salads, fresh-squeezed organic juices, smoothies, and organic coffee bar.
